quran[22{c,v,t}:
85,1,aasman ki qasam jis mein burj hain
85,2,aur is din ki jis ka wada hai
85,3,aur haazir honay walay ki aur jo is ke paas haazirkiya jaye uski
85,4,ke khndqon ( ke khodnay ) walay halaak kar diye gay
85,5,( yani ) aag ( ki khandaqein ) jis mein eendhan ( jhonk rakha ) tha
85,6,jab ke woh un ( ke kinaroon ) par baithy hue they
85,7,aur jo ( skhtyan ) ahal imaan par kar rahay they un ko samnay dekh rahay they
85,8,un ko mominon ki yahi baat buri lagti thi ke woh khuda par imaan laaye hue they jo ghalib ( aur ) qabil sataish hai
85,9,wohi jis ki asmano aur zameen mein badshahat hai. aur khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
85,10,jin logon ne momin mardon aur momin aurton ko takleifein den aur tauba nah ki un ko dozakh ka ( aur ) azaab bhi hoga aur julne ka azaab bhi hoga
85,11,( aur ) jo log imaan laaye aur naik kaam karte rahay un ke liye baagaat hain jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain. yeh hi barri kamyabi hai
85,12,be shak tumahray perwar-digaar ki pakar barri sakht hai
85,13,wohi pehli dafaa peda karta hai aur wohi dobarah ( zindah ) kere ga
85,14,aur woh bakhsnay wala aur mohabbat karne wala hai
85,15,arsh ka maalik barri shaan wala
85,16,jo chahta hai kar deta hai
85,17,bhala tum ko lashkaron ka haal maloom howa hai
85,18,( yani ) firaon aur smod ka
85,19,lekin kafir ( jaan boojh kar ) takzieeb mein ( girftar ) hain
85,20,aur khuda ( bhi ) un ko gurda gird se ghairay hue hai
85,21,( yeh kitaab hazal o batlan nahi ) balkay yeh quran azeem al shan hai
85,22,looh mehfooz mein ( likha howa )
